    "data": [
        {
            "title": "Jeffrey頸部受傷後首度露面 唔怕留疤自嘲買重保險 獲一班《膠戰》拍檔關心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/79d5049e18e9db7981584cb3dad83da6/2025-05/JEFF_0.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/a0a76d392b4971f0802236a5e8aa0102/15a50ed838754950a5c92d5489a80fcc-ab94412d08323703441d3c8825e18429-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681b65f826fd8\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-681b65f826fd9\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"Jeffrey頸部受傷後首度露面 唔怕留疤自嘲買重保險 獲一班《膠戰》拍檔關心\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3cb8797b181d712af9a430bf81f76b2d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250507/_2025050721422560990.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">Jeffrey頸部受傷後首度露面 唔怕留疤自嘲買重保險 獲一班《膠戰》拍檔關心</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>魏浚笙（Jeffrey）早前拍攝電影期間受傷，今晚首度露面在澳門出席活動，Jeffrey顯得很精神，脖子兩邊都貼上膠布，沒有露出傷口，問到傷勢他指是康復當中，需要每日消毒。\n\n</p><h2>憶述事件經過</h2>\n<p>問到Jeffrey事發經過？他指正忙於為運動題材電影拍攝，由於拍攝滑水時不能放開手把，當他跌入水中時手把連着的繩繞了他的脖子一圈，當時船正在運行因此被勒住了幾秒鐘，當下獲劇組及船家協助消毒並送院，已確定頸骨沒受傷。問下刻有否怕窒息，他表示有，幸好順利鬆開繩子，當下亦腦海一片空白，得知流血有少少驚，幸不用縫針。Jeffrey表示將會補拍該鏡頭，等康復後才會拍攝，時間是以星期計算，因此現在乖乖聽醫生指示。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey受傷後，今晚首度露面在澳門出席活動，同場還有林嘉欣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d262b9d2ff4bcb2a2fd3ddf7d0b14ba7/2025-05/_DSC4358.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey受傷後，今晚首度露面在澳門出席活動，同場還有林嘉欣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey脖子兩邊都貼上膠布。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a133591daa296428bf374828359a7169/2025-05/_DSC4363.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey脖子兩邊都貼上膠布。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"精神睇嚟唔錯。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64cfcbd7f28b6f4713144789632c4071/2025-05/_DSC4370.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        精神睇嚟唔錯。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey指現正康復當中，需要每日消毒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d0e3e1c799468ab915deb2d93b63ad7/2025-05/_DSC4465.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey指現正康復當中，需要每日消毒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey說當時流血有少少驚，幸不用縫針。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2fd1185d3112a5e65e16556089102edd/2025-05/_DSC4470.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey說當時流血有少少驚，幸不用縫針。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey表示往後買重保險，自己亦會小心，直言不太怕留疤。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d622f9527188aed35680d99d1e687eb5/2025-05/1_12.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey表示往後買重保險，自己亦會小心，直言不太怕留疤。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Jeffrey冧爆說女友每日幫他消毒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/79434ebbacc7e7395dc39f566a84a28e/2025-05/2_0_10.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Jeffrey冧爆說女友每日幫他消毒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"問可有生死一刻感覺，Jeffrey笑言沒有。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f34244e90d51674b0bbeef71226c9f03/2025-05/3_1_12.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        問可有生死一刻感覺，Jeffrey笑言沒有。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"一班《膠戰》拍檔都有關心他。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a35b93cc03ab2fbd4696b6fe9fa791e2/2025-05/4_0_16.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一班《膠戰》拍檔都有關心他。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>「男人有大條疤都可以！」</h2>\n<p>Jeffrey指演員所有事要克服，可能有少量工作因傷而影響，因算是簡單鏡頭，沒想到要安排替身演出，又笑言往後買重保險，自己亦會小心，直言不太怕留疤，更搞笑稱：「男人有大條疤都可以！」他表示電影已煞科，之後要補戲，問女友如何照顧他？他指女友每日幫他消毒，問可有生死一刻感覺，他笑言沒有，亦沒有影響新一季《膠戰》拍攝，一班拍檔都有關心他。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
