            "title": "中環雙屍案｜七旬夫婦伊利近街單位內燒炭亡 兒子揭發報警",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a646138beeaae2f38a8f0fb43ddc26ff/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250507/_2025050721375465511.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>中環發生夫婦燒炭自殺案。今日（7日）晚上8時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指其父母於伊利近街52號一單位內燒炭，救援人員到場證實二人當場不治，死因有待驗屍確定。消息指，兩人年約70多歲，初步警方在單位內發現一盤已燒過的炭，但未有發現遺書，正了解其二人輕生原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235823/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方封鎖現場調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d31a8a1d3ba2c555fcecaeae6736e67/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_31_45_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方封鎖現場調查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235824/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方封鎖現場調查。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3feb85993be7902c654e88a6578a95d8/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_31_45.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方封鎖現場調查。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235825/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為中環伊利近街52號一單位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7dc254da8ab27f999c9e27a5a20674d8/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_31_46_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為中環伊利近街52號一單位。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235826/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在中環伊利近街52號一單位發現一對夫婦燒炭亡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/100c85f3103d47e097a84bfdb391b2e8/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_31_46.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在中環伊利近街52號一單位發現一對夫婦燒炭亡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235827/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一對夫婦在中環伊利近街52號一單位燒炭亡。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8578ed44a2f7f2a245a46a67c6fd17be/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_34_20_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一對夫婦在中環伊利近街52號一單位燒炭亡。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235828/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為中環伊利近街52號一單位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/15a92588db42450e4978cb7fa1db179f/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_21_34_20.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為中環伊利近街52號一單位。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>防止自殺求助熱線：<br/>\n「情緒通」精神健康支援熱線：18111<br/>\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br/>\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br/>\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br/>\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br/>\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br/>\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br/>\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br/>\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open 噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\">http://www.openup.hk</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
