            "title": "東涌白貓墮樓 全身濕透當場死亡 警設法聯絡貓主",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/87a843ae06a5303bc5e2b1fc8ef3ed91/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250507/_2025050720470597436.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（7日）晚上7時許，一隻白貓從東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓的高處墮下，保安發現後報警求助。由於當時正下雨，白貓全貓濕透，並痛苦哀鳴，警員到場後證實白貓已經死亡，正設法聯絡飼主調查白貓墮樓原因。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235729/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"現場為東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/44632a83acb2b552ba0170b1b2c10adb/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_20_27_01_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        現場為東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235730/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一隻白貓從東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓的高處墮下。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4dcb73e6db0e963616c4e10db53462a5/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_20_27_01_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一隻白貓從東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓的高處墮下。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235731/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一隻白貓從東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓的高處墮下。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/64429a0059bca6510589f03c84c98ba5/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_20_27_01_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一隻白貓從東涌逸東邨瑞逸樓的高處墮下。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235732/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"白貓全貓濕透，痛苦哀鳴。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c35278270c2b636efa8c618944e5869/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_20_27_01.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        白貓全貓濕透，痛苦哀鳴。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4235733/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"保安發現後報警求助。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d8cadf2ad62b00be099dc1c140b8f83b/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-07_at_20_27_00.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保安發現後報警求助。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
